--------------------------------------------------

Please improve the overall appearance.

Suggestions:

Bootstrap cards

Rounded corners

Consistent spacing

Icons where appropriate

Sticky toolbar

Better typography

Responsive layout

The application should feel like a polished internal reporting tool rather than a prototype.

